Document: class_skeletonprofilehumanoid
Path: godot/classes/class_skeletonprofilehumanoid.rst
Summary: Properties overriding SkeletonProfile settings for bone grouping and scaling in humanoid skeletons.

bone_size (int): overrides SkeletonProfile's bone_size. Default: 56.
group_size (int): overrides SkeletonProfile's group_size. Default: 4.
root_bone (StringName): overrides SkeletonProfile's root_bone. Default: &"Root".
scale_base_bone (StringName): overrides SkeletonProfile's scale_base_bone. Default: &"Hips".